Saṃyutta Nikāya 35 
1. Aniccavagga 
3. Ajjhattānattasutta 
“Cakkhuṃ, bhikkhave, anattā. 
Yadanattā taṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ. 
Sotaṃ anattā … pe … 
ghānaṃ anattā … 
jivhā anattā … 
kāyo anattā … 
mano anattā. 
Yadanattā taṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya daṭṭhabbaṃ. 
Evaṃ passaṃ … pe … 
nāparaṃ itthattāyāti pajānātī”ti. 
Tatiyaṃ. 
